document.full_text: a jump shot by the wildcats' brandon knight with 5.4 seconds to play sent kentucky to the east regional final and sent the third no. 1 seed of the tournament home for the season.
document.title: east: kentucky 62, ohio state 60: kentucky climbs as another no. 1 falls
